---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 534
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Prayer-Meditation-Contemplation=On Concentration
  - 618
By: Mechthild of Magdeburg
---
Whosoever should hold himself straightly in the ‘puli’ which comes
from God and follow after the light as he sees it. would come to such
bliss and heavenly knowledge that no heart could contain it. Then he
would be as an angel, ever lovingly united to God in all things.
